<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/254282-ok-ok-ok-i-know-this-is-vague-and">Ok, ok, ok.. i know this is vague and redundant, but is this a good read? I am looking for something dark, not a &quot;lovey-dovey-im-an-emotional-preteen-oh-does-he-really-love-me&quot; YA novel that is so annoyingly prevalent these days.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_254282'><a id="like_count_community_question_254282" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/254282?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">28 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F10194157-shadow-and-bone">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/254282-ok-ok-ok-i-know-this-is-vague-and">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/254282-ok-ok-ok-i-know-this-is-vague-and">See all 19 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
